Pride Inn Group Hotels Managing Director Hasnain Noorani has reported an increase in business events as the year comes to a close. "November looks very optimistic and positive, we are still hosting meetings, investments, incentives and businesses in Mombasa," he said. He added that they are also hosting leisure travellers due to the Safari Theme Aqua Park. “We also have many firms, corporates and NGOs that are planning for 2019, and this is making us busy.” He said the hotel has recorded many bookings for Christmas dinners, End of Year parties, team building, among others.  